{"tid":1436422,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[加拿大］ trans唔transfer 好？","createTime":"2019-08-09T09:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T23:06:59.000Z","uid":214079,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"85562ce08e8314ee82ddf2c689bda855fd4060f3","tid":1436422,"uid":214079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"事源自己本身讀緊u of Manitoba CS<br />\n上年就apply 左transfer 去Alberta咁岩岩收左 <br />\n但係就15 16 唔知去唔去好<br />\n<br />\n名氣好似好小小 同埋貴小小<br />\n<br />\nps. 大部份credit 都trans 到 <br />\n<br />\n本身想讀完undergrad 去美國讀master 既， transfer左會唔會有咩幫助？<br />\n<br />\n 唔該哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4387cda6334dc5f7efbe5dc3a4f2eb808734fe4","tid":1436422,"uid":214079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbeac2b44ba7bfabcb718f8ea73d8cdec39d8d0","tid":1436422,"uid":214079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6079d033d90676cb6e1efb1bb4d3a8d1f944354","tid":1436422,"uid":214079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f763ee12a1a080eb2d94356f50ec01bf443b45","tid":1436422,"uid":274136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:26:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各有各做<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重點日程：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月9-11日</strong>：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月10日</strong>：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span>"},{"pid":"1bfbbc110a889234bfb784d42aed3b6477559366","tid":1436422,"uid":214079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T21:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac535fb7e09339c597f32c3163f028b68251858","tid":1436422,"uid":214079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T22:36:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"417a5210dc7124de475946de01dd30e4cbff59ce","tid":1436422,"uid":284491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:11:04.000Z","msg":"transfer 去 ubc or u of t"},{"pid":"d287db159d48ef67ce2f73aa6c71e96dd8080c3b","tid":1436422,"uid":229803,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:21:31.000Z","msg":"如果係我就唔trans<br />\n其實唔會話因爲學校嘅名氣而搵工易咗<br />\n(除非你係另一個麥明詩)<br />\n好多employer都睇work experience<br />\n愈多work experience 愈好<br />\n因為佢地覺得周街都係大學生 <br />\n唔會因為你覺得嘅所謂名氣好少少<br />\n而請你 分分鐘請咗個名氣冇咁好<br />\n但係work experience 多過你嘅人<br />\n無謂嘥錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e96607b87a54078071669f130639dad40b606af","tid":1436422,"uid":303466,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:01:37.000Z","msg":"巴打原本加籍定咩 據我所知manitoba係比較容易畢業後移民嘅省"},{"pid":"1d60636c378d41111fa7246e3873e6d856a6d15e","tid":1436422,"u